m2017profes-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-baum2017profes_3-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-baum2017profes_3-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-baum2017profes_3-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403\"><cite id=\"CITEREFBaumLeßmannSchneider2017\" class=\"citation book cs1\">Baum, Tobias; Leßmann, Hendrik; Schneider, Kurt (2017). \"The Choice of Code Review Process: A Survey on the State of the Practice\". <i>Product-Focused Software Process Improvement</i>. Lecture Notes in Computer Science. Vol.&#160;10611. pp.&#160;111–127. <a href=\"/wiki/Doi_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Doi (identifier)\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1007%2F978-3-319-69926-4_9\">10.1007/978-3-319-69926-4_9</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"ISBN (identifier)\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-3-319-69925-7\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-3-319-69925-7\"><bdi>978-3-319-69925-7</bdi></a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=The+Choice+of+Code+Review+Process%3A+A+Survey+on+the+State+of+the+Practice&amp;rft.btitle=Product-Focused+Software+Process+Improvement&amp;rft.series=Lecture+Notes+in+Computer+Science&amp;rft.pages=111-127&amp;rft.date=2017&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1007%2F978-3-319-69926-4_9&amp;rft.isbn=978-3-319-69925-7&amp;rft.aulast=Baum&amp;rft.aufirst=Tobias&amp;rft.au=Le%C3%9Fmann%2C+Hendrik&amp;rft.au=Schneider%2C+Kurt&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACode+review\" class=\"Z3988\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-bacchelli2013icse-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-bacchelli2013icse_4-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-bacchelli2013icse_4-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403\"><cite id=\"CITEREFBacchelliBird2013\" class=\"citation web cs1\">Bacchelli, A; Bird, C (May 2013). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sback.it/publications/icse2013.pdf\">\"Expectations, outcomes, and challenges of modern code review\"</a> <span class=\"cs1-format\">(PDF)</span>. Proceedings of the 35th IEEE/ACM International Conference On Software Engineering (ICSE 2013)<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2015-09-02</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Expectations%2C+outcomes%2C+and+challenges+of+modern+code+review&amp;rft.pub=Proceedings+of+the+35th+IEEE%2FACM+International+Conference+On+Software+Engineering+%28ICSE+2013%29&amp;rft.date=2013-05&amp;rft.aulast=Bacchelli&amp;rft.aufirst=A&amp;rft.au=Bird%2C+C&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fsback.it%2Fpublications%2Ficse2013.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACode+review\" class=\"Z3988\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-baum2016fse-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-baum2016fse_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403\"><cite id=\"CITEREFBaumLiskinNiklasSchneider2016\" class=\"citation book cs1\">Baum, Tobias; Liskin, Olga; Niklas, Kai; Schneider, Kurt (2016). \"Factors Influencing Code Review Processes in Industry\". <i>Proceedings of the 2016 24th ACM SIGSOFT International Symposium on Foundations of Software Engineering - FSE 2016</i>. pp.&#160;85–96. <a href=\"/wiki/Doi_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Doi (identifier)\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1145%2F2950290.2950323\">10.114