iki/Special:BookSources/978-0-7381-5768-9\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-7381-5768-9\"><bdi>978-0-7381-5768-9</bdi></a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=IEEE+Standard+for+Software+Reviews+and+Audits&amp;rft.pages=1-53&amp;rft.pub=IEEE+STD+1028-2008&amp;rft.date=2008-08&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1109%2Fieeestd.2008.4601584&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-7381-5768-9&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fieeexplore.ieee.org%2Fdocument%2F4601584&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACode+review\" class=\"Z3988\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-fagan1976-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-fagan1976_7-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-fagan1976_7-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403\"><cite id=\"CITEREFFagan1976\" class=\"citation journal cs1\">Fagan, Michael (1976). \"Design and code inspections to reduce errors in program development\". <i>IBM Systems Journal</i>. <b>15</b> (3): 182–211. <a href=\"/wiki/Doi_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Doi (identifier)\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1147%2Fsj.153.0182\">10.1147/sj.153.0182</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=IBM+Systems+Journal&amp;rft.atitle=Design+and+code+inspections+to+reduce+errors+in+program+development&amp;rft.volume=15&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=182-211&amp;rft.date=1976&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1147%2Fsj.153.0182&amp;rft.aulast=Fagan&amp;rft.aufirst=Michael&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACode+review\" class=\"Z3988\"></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-rigby2013fse-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-rigby2013fse_8-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"r